le:none} }</style><div class=\"productContentBlockMain\" data-content-type=\"row\" data-appearance=\"full-bleed\" data-enable-parallax=\"0\" data-parallax-speed=\"0.5\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-background-type=\"image\" data-video-loop=\"true\" data-video-play-only-visible=\"true\" data-video-lazy-load=\"true\" data-video-fallback-src=\"\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"SAU29Y8\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-group\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-content-type=\"column-group\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-grid-size=\"12\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"OTYFH9S\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-line\" data-content-type=\"column-line\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"U7MOYWA\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column title\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"GK2MH14\"><h2 data-content-type=\"heading\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\">除了财务报告、财务指标以外，为了更广阔的未来。</h2></div><div class=\"pagebuilder-column content\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"TDMWPD8\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p class=\"MachineTrans-lang-zh-CN\">该报告是根据IFRS和GRI标准制定的，该义务适用于在受监管市场上交易的上市公司以及非金融和公司可持续报告的准则。我们的方法使我们作为一家企业创造的价值和影响更大：除了财务报告、财务指标以外，为了更广阔的未来。</p>\r\n<p class=\"MachineTrans-lang-zh-CN\">您可能会在此报告中注意到贝卡尔特的一些独特之处：我们已经启用了新的愿景和使命，以及一套新的视觉标识系统，以将我们的企业文化与大胆创新结合在一起的方式代表我们的品牌。在我们悠久的历史上，开启新的篇章，具有雄心勃勃的价值主张，明确的使命和大胆的新品牌风格。</p></div><div data-content-type=\"html\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\">&lt;div class=\"widget\"&gt;\r\n    &lt;a href=\"https://dev-api.bekaert.cn/media/wysiwyg/files/annual-report/Bekaert-Annual-Report-2022.pdf\" class=\"btn-link download-file-events\" style=\"margin-left: 0;\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;下载年度报告&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;</div></div></div></div><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-group contentWithImage\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-content-type=\"column-group\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-grid-size=\"12\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"BQWQ6LN\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-line\" data-content-type=\"column-line\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"G6EEXIF\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column content-media\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"W3YNIKG\"><figure data-content-type=\"image\" data-appearance=\"full-width\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"EXR4KF8\"><img class=\"pagebuilder-mobile-hidden\" src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/3101_5P1A1863_RGB.png}}\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" data-image-dimensions=\"{&quot;height&quot;:620,&quot;width&quot;:877,&quot;ratio&quot;:0.71}\" data-element=\"desktop_image\" data-pb-style=\"D37TOPJ\"><img class=\"pagebuilder-mobile-only\" src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/3101_5P1A1863_RGB.png}}\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" data-image-dimensions=\"{&quot;height&quot;:620,&quot;width&quot;:877,&quot;ratio&quot;:0.71}\" data-element=\"mobile_image\" data-pb-style=\"OOR9LGN\"></figure></div><div class=\"pagebuilder-column\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"NSOI1UT\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><h3 class=\"content-title\">董事长和首席执行官致辞</h3>\r\n<p>尽管面临许多全球挑战，但我们很高兴地宣布2022年的战略性进展和强劲的财务业绩。我们通过有效的定价策略，产品组合调整，抓住业务增长机会，和提高组织效率来实现这一目标，以抵消能源和材料成本的大幅上升。</p></div><div data-content-type=\"html\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\">&lt;div class=\"widget\"&gt;\r\n    &lt;a href=\"/annual-report/2022/message-from-the-chairman-and-the-ceo\" class=\"btn-link click-link-events\" style=\"margin-left: 0;\"&gt;阅读完整消息&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;</div></div></div></div><h2 data-content-type=\"heading\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"MSQWKL9\">2022年的亮点</h2><figure class=\"full_wide\" data-content-type=\"image\" data-appearance=\"full-width\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"TQBOSXP\"><img class=\"pagebuilder-mobile-hidden\" src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/3215_Capitals_Infographic_2023_V5_RGB.png}}\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" data-image-dimensions=\"{&quot;height&quot;:1060,&quot;width&quot;:1500,&quot;ratio&quot;:0.71}\" data-element=\"desktop_image\" data-pb-style=\"MUY7OF0\"><img class=\"pagebuilder-mobile-only\" src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/3215_Capitals_Infographic_2023_V5_RGB.png}}\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" data-image-dimensions=\"{&quot;height&quot;:1060,&quot;width&quot;:1500,&quot;ratio&quot;:0.71}\" data-element=\"mobile_image\" data-pb-style=\"KJ835OL\"></figure><h2 data-content-type=\"heading\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"NCMCWJR\">综合年度报告2022</h2><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-group annual-report\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-content-type=\"column-group\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-grid-size=\"12\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"HGNFIE8\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-line\" data-content-type=\"column-line\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"R8PUI0C\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"MT31NXM\"><div class=\"main-wrap\" data-content-type=\"content_card\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-appearance-type=\"vertical\" data-element=\"main\"><div class=\"img-wrapper\"><figure><img class=\"pagebuilder-mobile-hidden\" src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/4100_GettyImages-1328813952_RGB.png}}\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" data-element=\"desktop_image\" data-pb-style=\"EO53D2F\"><img class=\"pagebuilder-mobile-only\" src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/4100_GettyImages-1328813952_RGB.png}}\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" da