\n        }\r\n\r\n        .news-lister .row-full-width-inner .news-item {\r\n            width: auto;\r\n            margin: 0 0 24px 0;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .news-lister .row-full-width-inner {\r\n            width: auto !important;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .news-lister-title .row-full-width-inner {\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n            width: 100% !important;\r\n            box-sizing: border-box;\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n&lt;/style&gt;</div><div class=\"productContentBlockMain\" data-content-type=\"row\" data-appearance=\"full-bleed\" data-enable-parallax=\"0\" data-parallax-speed=\"0.5\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-background-type=\"image\" data-video-loop=\"true\" data-video-play-only-visible=\"true\" data-video-lazy-load=\"true\" data-video-fallback-src=\"\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"U62K2Q3\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-group\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-content-type=\"column-group\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-grid-size=\"12\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"HV4N39B\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-line\" data-content-type=\"column-line\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"X69OE99\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column title\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"VJ9F2K9\"><h2 data-content-type=\"heading\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\">水是生命之源</h2></div><div class=\"pagebuilder-column content click-link-events red-link\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"DRM7G10\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p class=\"MachineTrans-lang-zh-CN\">通过河流和运河的垃圾不断流入，每年有110亿公斤的塑料垃圾通过河流汇入到海洋。这对海洋生物和我们所有人都产生了毁灭性的影响。</p>\r\n<p class=\"MachineTrans-lang-zh-CN\">我们旨在以最佳方式支持当地社区。仅处理我们的排废还不够。因此，我们于2022年与<a tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https://www.river-cleanup.org/en\">River Cleanup</a>合作。</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-group bulleted-list-check content contentWithImage\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-content-type=\"column-group\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-grid-size=\"12\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"M1I3QF1\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-line\" data-content-type=\"column-line\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"A7GVKDG\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column content\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"DNYUGQ4\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p class=\"MachineTrans-lang-zh-CN\">2022年6月27日在<strong>比利时</strong>是一个晴天。贝卡尔特同事们聚集在<strong>比利时贝卡尔特总部附近的斯凯尔特河岸</strong>。</p>\r\n<p class=\"MachineTrans-lang-zh-CN\">他们参加河道清理活动，在当地消防员和大自然保护组织的支持下，从河道及河岸捡拾垃圾。</p>\r\n<p class=\"MachineTrans-lang-zh-CN\">大家从河道通过钓鱼船，走在河岸边捡拾，共收集了71公斤的垃圾。</p></div></div><div class=\"pagebuilder-column content-media\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"XW8618D\"><figure data-content-type=\"image\" data-appearance=\"full-width\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"MH87FGN\"><img class=\"pagebuilder-mobile-hidden\" src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/belgium_riverleandup2.png}}\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" data-image-dimensions=\"{&quot;height&quot;:696,&quot;width&quot;:1000,&quot;ratio&quot;:0.7}\" data-element=\"desktop_image\" data-pb-style=\"XMONWXL\"><img class=\"pagebuilder-mobile-only\" src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/belgium_riverleandup2.png}}\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" data-image-dimensions=\"{&quot;height&quot;:696,&quot;width&quot;:1000,&quot;ratio&quot;:0.7}\" data-element=\"mobile_image\" data-pb-style=\"DFIEBFS\"></figure></div></div></div><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-group bulleted-list-check content contentWithImage\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-content-type=\"column-group\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-grid-size=\"12\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"FTTWW3M\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-line\" data-content-type=\"column-line\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"UW7HHC0\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column content-media\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"WRGNO79\"><figure data-content-type=\"image\" data-appearance=\"full-width\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"DFXUN2U\"><img class=\"pagebuilder-mobile-hidden\" src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/Bekaert-Lake_Cleanup_2022.png}}\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" data-image-dimensions=\"{&quot;height&quot;:712,&quot;width&quot;:949,&quot;ratio&quot;:0.75}\" data-element=\"desktop_image\" data-pb-style=\"QO4J9E7\"><img class=\"pagebuilder-mobile-only\" src=\"{{media url=wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/Bekaert-Lake_Cleanup_2022.png}}\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" data-image-dimensions=\"{&quot;height&quot;:712,&quot;width&quot;:949,&quot;ratio&quot;:0.75}\" data-element=\"mobile_image\" data-pb-style=\"VIAR5LY\"></figure></div><div class=\"pagebuilder-column content\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"KKUOPRA\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p class=\"MachineTrans-lang-zh-CN\">我们位于<strong>阿肯色州范布伦市</strong>的同事们于2022年9月在城市的<strong>Lou Emma湖</strong>上举行了类似的垃圾清理活动。</p>\r\n<p class=\"MachineTrans-lang-zh-CN\">湖泊虽然与海洋没有连接，但也是塑料和其他垃圾污染的水域，无论是在盆地和连接的小溪中水质的恶化，都将影响到动物和植物的生物多样性。</p>\r\n<p class=\"MachineTrans-lang-zh-CN\">团队成员们辛勤劳动了一个早晨，共清除了大约55公斤的垃圾。</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-group quote\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-content-type=\"column-group\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-grid-size=\"12\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"VSYM5JW\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column-line\" data-content-type=\"column-line\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"AL67ONE\"><div class=\"pagebuilder-column\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"W6HFFBL\"></div><div class=\"pagebuilder-column content\" data-content-type=\"column\" data-appearance=\"full-height\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"QH8G8F3\"><div data-content-type=\"html\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\">&lt;div class=\"text-wrapper col-sm-7\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"quote-text\"&gt;&lt;p&gt;这两个活动是一个很好的开始。我们已经在计划下一场活动，该活动将于2023年初在Citarum河上进行，这是世界上污染最严重的河流之一。我们希望能够吸引更多社区成员来一起参加，共同减少全球水污染的影响。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; \r\n&lt;div class=\"text-wrap\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"wrap\"&gt; \r\n&lt;div class=\"half-text\"&gt; &lt;p class=\"p-text\"&gt;Katelijn Bohez&lt;/p&gt; &lt;span&gt;可持续金融和社区关系副总裁&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;img src=\"https://dev-api.bekaert.cn/media/wysiwyg/cms/page/sustainability/Katelijn_Bohez_klein.png\" alt=\"Katelijn Bohez\"&gt;\r\n &lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"home-news\" data-content-type=\"row\" data-appearance=\"full-bleed\" data-enable-parallax=\"0\" data-parallax-speed=\"0.5\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-background-type=\"image\" data-video-loop=\"true\" data-video-play-only-visible=\"true\" data-video-lazy-load=\"true\" data-video-fallback-src=\"\" data-element=\"main\" data-pb-style=\"LNXJ3GM\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>{{widget type=\"Bekaert\\Cms\\Block\\Widget\\HomeNews\" template=\"Bekaert_Cms::widget/home_news.phtml\" node_id1=\"342\" node_id1_order=\"desc\" node_id2=\"343\" node_id2_order=\"desc\" node_id3=\"344\" node_id3_order=\"desc\" node_id4=\"363\" node_id4_order=\"asc\" title_text=\"新闻\" load_more_text=\"查看更多\" load_more_link=\"about-us/news-room\" read_detail_text=\"了解更多\"}}</p></div></div><div data-cont